item.title: CVE-2021-28173|2024-09-16T22:55:37.530Z -- vangene -- deltaflow%20e-platform
item.description: The file upload function of Vangene deltaFlow E-platform does not perform access controlled properly. Remote attackers can upload and execute arbitrary files without login.
